ui.comp3111

Class MainScreen

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.comp3111.MainScreen

  • public class MainScreen
extends java.lang.Object
    MainScreen - Primary Pane class in the GUI Application. All panes and nodes are generated in the main Pane and passed to the Main class to generate the JavaFX Scene. MainScreen class uses BorderPane object to put all the nodes in bordered layout (center, left, right, top).

      • pane

        public javafx.scene.layout.Pane pane()
        Pane function. Gets all the required nodes and layout them in the main pane. The pane is then passed to the Main class for scene generation. Contains : Import/Export, Datasets-Charts lists, Table Display, Chart Display, Chart Type Selector, Filter/Transformation.
        Returns:
        Pane object containing the main view of the GUI layout.
